title: "DMAIC Bootstrap"
authors:
  - family-names: Fahl
    given-names: Wolfgang
    orcid: "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-0821-6995"
    affiliation: "BITPlan GmbH, Willich, Germany"
abstract: >-
  Paper repository for the DMAIC Bootstrap experiment: applying the Six Sigma
  DMAIC cycle to LLM agent incidents recorded in a Semantic MediaWiki
  knowledge graph, and bootstrapping the improvement system by its own
  method. Content authoring is issue-gated per AGENTS.md; the
  scientific-content gate was opened by the human authors on 2026-07-13.
keywords:
  - "DMAIC"
  - "Six Sigma"
  - "LLM Agents"
  - "Semantic MediaWiki"
  - "Knowledge Graph"
